ActBroadcasting Act
SubjectCanadian Broadcasting Corporation ** Purchase and sale of property **
PrecisOrder approving that the CANADIAN BROADCASTING CORPORATION (as vendor) enter into an AGREEMENT of purchase and sale with CAMERON LAND CORPORATION (as purchaser) and into an assignment and assumption AGREEMENT (in which Cameron Land Corporation will assign its rights to SAXONY GLEN LTD.) to dispose of real property located at 3245 -170 Street in Edmonton, Alberta.
